title: can braum block twitch's e pull?
body: because it comes out as a ray of strings, can braum intercept all of those? I can't find much info on what exactly constitutes as a projectile among the things that look like projectiles but actually are only visually so like annie and cho'gath's Ws.

replies.body:
no. twitch E is something that generates out of the target


like Vlad Q, only thing u can block from vlad q is the return heal
It's not a projectile , Braum E basically blocks what Yasuo w blocks
